dl.dd: This icon was drawn to replace the old icon shown on the far right side.
While the new icon is perfect symmetric, the old icon isn't.
It's 8 gaps are of different widths, the topmost ones disappear.
It is W3C-invalid and consists of embedded raster graphics, bloating it to a huge file size that can hold the size of the new one more than 565 times.
